sg":"天文台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://d.blog.xuite.net/d/2/5/5/10647735/blog_1062274/txt/16681151/0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd.blog.xuite.net%2Fd%2F2%2F5%2F5%2F10647735%2Fblog_1062274%2Ftxt%2F16681151%2F0.jpg&h=29db6076&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74833a43df23f53878480e6754cdf8c2127c8434","tid":1140663,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T04:12:37.000Z","msg":"咁大工程 決定行邊條頻道之前有考慮過吓話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a12e168c4d41cc6213d6a7935815ab4a53096d","tid":1140663,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T08:47:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: purple;\"></span>"},{"pid":"fe3547cb57d183ab2d40c33a27b2b30f9ff49b0b","tid":1140663,"uid":3068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47cd2adc902a174128e0df06eb20e6b411d106c7","tid":1140663,"uid":197337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T04:09:28.000Z","msg":"天文台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://d.blog.xuite.net/d/2/5/5/10647735/blog_1062274/txt/16681151/0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd.blog.xuite.net%2Fd%2F2%2F5%2F5%2F10647735%2Fblog_1062274%2Ftxt%2F16681151%2F0.jpg&h=29db6076&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T09:02:18.000Z","msg":"準過大交合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}